The paper deals with feature subset selection, which is a common problem in machine learning and data mining. The use of mutual information as a measure function suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), or cs.IT (Information Theory). The focus on search strategies and optimization further supports these sub-categories. Among these, cs.LG is the most likely sub-category as it is specifically dedicated to machine learning research.
